    S:gt.blockmachines.algaefarm.controller.tier.single.tooltip=Machine Type: §eAlgae Pond§r\nGrows Algae!\nProvide compost to boost production by one tier\nDoes not require power or maintenance\nAll Machine Casings must be the same tier, this dictates machine speed\nFill Input Hatch with Water to fill the inside of the multiblock\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
