    S:gt.blockmachines.chemicalplant.controller.tier.single.name=ExxonMobil Chemical Plant
    S:gt.blockmachines.chemicalplant.controller.tier.single.tooltip=Machine Type: §eChemical Plant§r\nHeavy Industry, now right at your doorstep!\nPlant tier is determined by casing tier\nHatch tiers can't be higher than machine casing tier, UHV casing unlocks all tiers\n§62§7 Parallels per §fPipe Casing§7 Tier\n+20% chance of not damaging catalyst per §f§fPipe Casing§7§7 Tier\nSpeed is §a50%§7 times §fHeating Coil§7 Tier\nAny catalyst must be placed in the catalyst housing\nAwakened Draconium coils combined with Tungstensteel pipe casing makes catalyst unbreakable\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.chemicalplant.controller.tier.single.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §67§7x§67§7x§67§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§f   Catalyst Housing: §7Any Casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6casing§r§7 for §6metal machine casing (minimum 70)\n   Uses sub channel §6machine_casing§r§7 for §6Machine Casing Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6coil§r§7 for §6Heating Coils Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6pipe§r§7 for §6Pipe Casing Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
