    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.em.computer.tooltip=Machine Type: §eQuantum Computer, QC§r\nController block of the Quantum Computer\nUsed to generate computation (and heat)\nUse screwdriver to toggle wireless mode\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.em.computer.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §62§7x§64§7x§65-16§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front left, 2nd layer\n§f   Uncertainty Resolver X: §7Any Computer Casing on the first or last slice\n§f   Data Connector: §7Any Computer Casing on the first or last slice\n§f   Computer Rack: §7Any Advanced Computer Casing, except the outer ones\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Computer Casing on the first or last slice\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Computer Casing on the first or last slice\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
