    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.transcendentplasmamixer.name=Transcendent Plasma Mixer
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.transcendentplasmamixer.tooltip=Machine Type: §eTranscendent Mixer, TPM§r\nAssisting in all your DTPF needs!\nThis multiblock will run in parallel according to the amount set in the parallel menu\nAll inputs will scale, except time...\nAll EU is deducted from wireless EU networks only\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§4§l§o§nC§6§l§o§no§a§l§o§nl§3§l§o§ne§5§l§o§nn§r§7
    S:gt.blockmachines.multimachine.transcendentplasmamixer.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §65§7x§67§7x§65§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) \n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§6   48x §r§7Dimensionally Transcendent Casing\n§6   16x §r§7Dimensional Bridge\n§6   0x§7 - §633x §r§7Dimensional Injection Casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Dimensional Injection Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Dimensional Injection Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Dimensional Injection Casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
