    S:gt.blockmachines.nuclearsaltprocessingplant.controller.tier.single.name=Nuclear Salt Processing Plant
    S:gt.blockmachines.nuclearsaltprocessingplant.controller.tier.single.tooltip=Machine Type: §eReactor Processing Unit, Cold Trap, NSPP§r\n§62§7 Parallels per §fVoltage§7 Tier\n§a250%§7 Speed\n§8100%§7 EU Usage\nProcesses depleted nuclear salts that come from the LFTR\nHandles the recipes of the Reactor Processor Unit and Cold Trap\nOnly Thermally Insulated Casings can be replaced with hatches\nMufflers on top, Energy Hatches on bottom, exactly 2 of each are required\nMaintenance Hatch goes on the back, opposite of the controller block\nInputs go on the left side of the multi, outputs on the right side\n§5500 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
