    S:gt.blockmachines.planetarygassiphon.tooltip=Machine Type: §ePump, PGS§r\n§4DEPRECATED - Controller will be removed in next major update!\n§4Check NEI for new Controller and conversion recipe\n§o%s\nBuild on a Space Station orbiting a Gas Planet\nRequires a Programmed Circuit set to the depth you want to pump from (1 - 4)\nRequires 64x depth Mining Pipes\nEU/t: d*4^(t+2), t is the Space Station's tier and d the depth\nCan load the chunk it is in (toggle using a Soldering Iron)\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
