    S:gt.blockmachines.thtr.name=Thorium High Temperature Reactor
    S:gt.blockmachines.thtr.tooltip=Machine Type: §eHigh Temperature Reactor, THTR§r\nNeeds to be primed with 730,000 of helium\nNeeds a constant supply of §bcoolant§7 while running\nNeeds at least §6100K§7 Fuel pebbles to start operation (can hold up to 675k pebbles)\nConsumes up to §60.5%§7 of total Fuel Pellets per Operation depending on efficiency\nEfficiency decreases exponentially if the internal buffer is not completely filled\nReactor will take §b4800L/t§7 of coolant multiplied by efficiency\nUses 3,840 EU/t\nOne Operation takes 9 hours\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
    S:gt.blockmachines.thtr.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §611§7x§612§7x§611§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front bottom center\n§6   500x §r§7Radiation Proof Casings (minimum)\n   Corners and the 2 touching blocks are air (cylindric)\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any top layer casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any top layer casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any bottom layer casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any bottom layer casing\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
